Class GamePanelEndedTournament

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class GamePanelEndedTournament
extends javafx.scene.layout.AnchorPane

    Class provides panels for an ended tournament containing the tournament's id, the tournaments name, the winner's name, possibility to look up the tournament's configuration and possibility to look up the tournament's scorelist.

        Constructs a panel with the tournament's id, the tournament's name, the winner's name, a possibility to look up the tournament's configuration and a possibility to look up the tournaments scorelist for an ended tournament.
        Parameters:
        tournamentID - id of the tournament the panel represents
        tournamentName - name of the tournament the panel represents
        winnerName - name of the winner of the tournament the panel represents
        config - configuration of the tournament the panel represents
        scoreList - scorelist of the tournament the panel represents
        vbox_gameList - vbox containing gamepanels of games belonging to tournament
